From c1fdeb677b2cf2bf16f50a935d90c0432891b63d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Leif Hedstrom <zwoop@apache.org>
Date: Tue, 15 Jun 2021 12:29:12 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] Adds bytes counting as a trigger to the cache_promote LRU
 (#7765)

* Refactoring and preparation to support bytes counting

* Fix naming of member variables, for consistency

* Add bytes counting as a trigger for LRU promotion

* Cleans up user data in TXN close

* Elimiantes the lookup call, so picky walt
